{
  "stem": "5891.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, of course, my sister Mathilde got sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister Mathilde never came out of that sick block.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could never get out of the sick block.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We walked around up there a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a little whistle my dad taught us when we were children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If we were lost or something, if you heard that whistle, that was for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a family whistle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody else-",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, I sure can.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if I still can do it right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll try.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[WHISTLES HIGH-PITCH FOLLOWED BY LOW-PITCH]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was such so long-- and you know, I taught my children that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I go in a shopping center, and I whistled, and my children automatic-- what, Ma?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm here!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Automatically.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I taught my children the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's the way my dad was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That whistle, we were kind of all recognized.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How did I get to that whistle?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You were trying to find your sister in the sick bay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the sick bay.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Going around there a little bit, thought maybe she was capable of somehow, maybe, you could-- see, on top of those booths, there were no windows in there, of course.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now we're talking about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not talking about Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm talking about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had [GERMAN], like in a bus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you could ventilate the top?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all there was in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a front door and the back door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no windows in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll tell you later in the story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You could look there, down a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somebody has to be a little bit more out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I thought, maybe, if she was up there-- because I knew, I was in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I knew how it worked.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
